{"tid":1371254,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"(代po) 領事館請願：請求英國制裁何君堯","createTime":"2019-07-27T08:37:41.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-29T07:42:25.000Z","uid":200200,"like":47,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"9da0eb8564178689a3cd986aecbf74ba8a7014d0","tid":1371254,"uid":200200,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T08:37:41.000Z","msg":"領事館請願：請求英國制裁何君堯<br />\n<br />\n（借account post嘢）<br />\n<br />\n元朗恐襲發生當日，何君堯親自到場支持同鼓勵恐怖分子，情況猶如監軍，親自督戰 。加上，喺元朗恐襲發生之前，何君堯就已經喺網上煽惑過，一啲不良分子去元朗襲擊民眾。好明顯，何君堯嚴重危害到香港人。既然效益主義係道德基礎，咁何君堯就係嚴重違反效益。<br />\n<br />\n爲咗保障香港人嘅幸福，所以我哋應該請求英國制裁何君堯，包括將佢列爲恐怖分子，褫奪佢英格蘭同威爾斯律師資格，禁止佢進入英國，充公佢喺英國嘅財產。希望大家可以一齊嚟英國駐香港領事館門口請願：<br />\n<br />\n日期：2019年7月29號（星期一）<br />\n時間：下晝3點<br />\n地點：英國駐香港總領事館門口<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/QDChgHb.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FQDChgHb.jpg&h=fbdb6ea3&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"92257d6fcfef11221e54032aec5d183518865908","tid":1371254,"uid":11436,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T08:40:29.000Z","msg":"推到何妖收皮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"65ee3fe55d7e850e1d099152e17089978eadec0b","tid":1371254,"uid":200200,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T11:21:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3a2d743a86734b995cddb276e983f349bccbba70","tid":1371254,"uid":115977,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T11:23:25.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"642fa7c13934e961a634f60a8196d24448c27657","tid":1371254,"uid":189058,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T11:45:59.000Z","msg":"push 呢單野一定要推撚爆佢"},{"pid":"fa6da95c376c9a82b22bf7561ec3c29dffd41ba8","tid":1371254,"uid":281824,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"9da0eb8564178